This is a responsive landing page project for PizzaFactory, a fictional pizza delivery brand. The page is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, featuring a visually appealing layout with a bold hero section, brand logo, and a clear call-to-action button.
The navigation bar allows users to smoothly explore different sections of the page. JavaScript has been used to add interactive elements such as dynamic scrolling behavior and menu link highlighting, enhancing the user experience. 
The design is optimized for various screen sizes, making it suitable for both desktop and mobile users.


